<br>
FT I adds 1 mana per tick - at my current level (51) I can equip it for it's full stats - and the FT I.  <br>
But...<br>
I have a mana pool of 2000 mana (maybe a little more, but for the sake of easy counting let's say 2k).  <br>
Per tick you get 20 mana (1 pct) - with he FT I item that makes it 21 mana - I dunno about you, but the 20 ticks for just 1pct mana extra at the cost for the earring... &lt;sigh&gt;.<br>
<br>
The general stats of the item are quite alright I guess, but I thought the FT I would add more manaregen then what I notice...<br>
<br>
Ach well, let's try and get more FT items (first I need to famr some pp though).<br>
<br>
Yanari Pethugger<br>
<br>
Dreading the prices for items with FT II to FT V on it.<br>
